      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "A petition is being circulated\namong the farmers, fruit growers and\ngardeners of the county asking the\ncity council to establish in Spokane\na public city market where all farm\nproducts can be offered for sale.\n\n\nThe farmers believe they will not\nonly benefit themselves, but also aid\nthe public by the establishment OF\nsuch a market. They claim that the\nquality of products will be greatly\nimproved by the open competition\na public market would afford.\n\n\n1t is planned to lay the petition\nbefore the council at it's next meet\ning,"
    }
